00:00:00.700 --> 00:00:05.460
On Monday, April 28 2014, the seventh grade of Laugalækjarskóli went,

00:00:05.460 --> 00:00:09.580
along with the seventh grade of Ölduselsskóli, on a trip to the Reykjaskóli School Camp.

00:00:10.180 --> 00:00:12.180
After giving it a lot of thought, I decided to go with the kids

00:00:12.180 --> 00:00:14.180
but decided that I should record a documentary on the trip,

00:00:14.180 --> 00:00:17.300
to help others decide for themselves whether they want to go there.

00:00:18.700 --> 00:00:21.900
When we arrived, most of our time went to getting everything set up

00:00:21.900 --> 00:00:24.860
so there isn't a lot to show from the first day.

00:00:24.860 --> 00:00:26.860
However, there are recordings of the kvöldvaka (evening program).

00:00:27.420 --> 00:00:30.260
There is a kvöldvaka (an evening program) daily at Reykjaskóli.

00:00:30.260 --> 00:00:33.500
